13:38.451 --> 13:41.352
Oh, Howard, he won't play
"Moonlight in Vermont."

13:41.487 --> 13:43.285
Would you fix him?

13:43.423 --> 13:45.255
What do you want me
to do, Marion?

13:45.391 --> 13:47.951
Well, pay him so that he will
play "Moonlight in Vermont."

13:48.094 --> 13:51.257
Well, why should I pay him if
he doesn't know how to play it?

13:51.397 --> 13:53.525
Now, listen, Marion,
I almost threw my back out

13:53.666 --> 13:56.067
