I could've gotten beaten up

13:56.202 --> 13:58.330
by a man who's cheating
on his wife, and now

13:58.471 --> 14:00.303
you want me to fix
the piano player.

14:00.440 --> 14:03.375
Now, that's asking an awful lot
for just an okay date, Marion.

14:03.509 --> 14:05.204
You know,
I really think it's silly

14:05.345 --> 14:06.870
