♪ Ooh... 'cause of you ♪

20:50.850 --> 20:53.182
♪ 'Cause of you ♪

20:54.820 --> 20:56.811
♪ 'Cause of you ♪

20:58.057 --> 21:00.048
♪ 'Cause of you ♪

21:01.093 --> 21:02.254
♪ 'Cause of you! ♪

21:02.394 --> 21:05.364
(cheering)

21:06.766 --> 21:07.756
Thank you, thank you.

21:07.900 --> 21:08.890
I have an announcement to make.

21:09.034 --> 21:09.899
Good news!

21:10.035 --> 21:11.469
The broken pipe at Arnold's

21:11.604 --> 21:12.628
is not that bad.

21:12.772 --> 21:13.967
Gonna be able to get it fixed

21:14.106 --> 21:15.835
and Al's gonna be back
in business tomorrow.

21:15.975 --> 21:17.568
- G reat, great!
-(cheering)

21:17.710 --> 21:19.439
Well, just-just
don't forget that, uh,

21:19.578 --> 21:21.307
we're able to use this house

21:21.447 --> 21:24.109
due to the courtesy
of Mom and Dad,

21:24.250 --> 21:26.912
who've donated the premises
in absentia.

21:27.052 --> 21:28.577
(laughing)

21:28.721 --> 21:31.622
Mom and Dad are
on their second honeymoon.

21:31.757 --> 21:33.452
ALL:
Ooh!

21:33.592 --> 21:34.684
Yeah.

21:34.827 --> 21:36.090
Yeah, they didn't get it
right the first time.

21:36.228 --> 21:37.423
- Ha ha.
-(laughter)

21:37.563 --> 21:39.588
Even in the Annex,
I still got it.

21:39.732 --> 21:41.598
I have an announcement to make.

21:41.734 --> 21:43.828
Even though we're in the Annex,

21:43.969 --> 21:46.904
ah, the quality of my food
will not suffer.

21:47.039 --> 21:49.007
I want you to know that
all the Arnoldburgers

21:49.141 --> 21:51.371
