22:00.152 --> 22:02.314
MARION:
Home sweet home, Howard.

22:02.454 --> 22:05.048
HOWARD:
What's <i>going</i> on in there?

22:10.863 --> 22:12.388
(music stops)

22:12.531 --> 22:13.464
All right!

22:13.599 --> 22:15.590
Thanks for the solo spot, guys.

22:18.370 --> 22:19.235
Cut it out.

22:19.371 --> 22:21.465
Well, thank you for the welcome.

22:21.607 --> 22:22.972
I'm overwhelmed!

22:23.108 --> 22:24.098
Marion...

22:28.948 --> 22:31.849
Richard, I'm sure there's
an explanation for this.

22:31.984 --> 22:33.145
Well, there is, there is.

22:33.285 --> 22:35.310
But, uh, man-to-man, Dad,

22:35.454 --> 22:36.853
how come you came home so
soon?

22:36.989 --> 22:38.855
Well, it's a long story,

22:38.991 --> 22:40.789
but a nice one,
right, Babycakes?

22:40.926 --> 22:43.088
Right, Snookums.

22:44.763 --> 22:47.460
You know how to play
"Moonlight in Vermont"?

22:47.600 --> 22:48.624
Yeah, sure we know it,

22:48.767 --> 22:50.166
