to hear that song.

22:50.302 --> 22:51.292
POTSIE:
Yeah, no one wants to hear that.

22:51.437 --> 22:53.428
FONZIE:
Hold it!

22:56.008 --> 22:57.498
This fabumondo couple

22:57.643 --> 22:58.940
is having
an anniversary tomorrow.

22:59.078 --> 23:01.547
It happens to be
one of my favorite tunes.

23:02.748 --> 23:04.011
Why don't you play them
their song, huh?

23:04.149 --> 23:05.913
- All right.
- All right.

23:06.051 --> 23:07.951
