23:12.157 --> 23:14.216
Just a little anniversary humor.

23:14.360 --> 23:15.657
Take it away.

23:36.448 --> 23:37.472
Good-bye.

23:37.616 --> 23:39.448
We'll do it again
tomorrow night.

23:39.585 --> 23:40.575
Marion!

23:44.490 --> 23:45.685
Well, don't worry.

23:45.824 --> 23:46.882
We-we'll clean everything up
tomorrow, and uh...

23:47.026 --> 23:48.221
Yeah, we'll clean everything up.

23:48.360 --> 23:49.919
Happy anniversary.

23:50.062 --> 23:51.461
I hope you enjoyed your present.

23:51.597 --> 23:54.658
Oh, Holiday Shores
was just beautiful.

23:54.800 --> 23:55.926
Thanks again, kids.

23:56.068 --> 23:57.467
That's okay.

23:57.603 --> 24:00.766
Well, uh, see you in
the morning, Mr. Okay.

24:00.906 --> 24:02.840
Good night, Mrs. Average.

24:05.177 --> 24:06.110
BOTH:
We love you.

24:06.245 --> 24:08.077
Oh, good night.

24:12.484 --> 24:16.751
What are you thinking of
at a time like this, Snookums?

24:16.889 --> 24:19.415
Food, Marion.

24:19.558 --> 24:21.117
We haven't eaten yet, remember?

24:21.260 --> 24:22.386
MARION: Oh, that's right.

24:22.528 --> 24:24.929
Uh, do you have any more
Arnoldburgers in there, Al?

24:25.064 --> 24:28.034
Oh, gee, Howard, I'd like
to fix something up for you,

24:28.167 --> 24:29.692
but I got a late date.

24:29.835 --> 24:31.064
There's a lot of food
in the refrigerator,

24:31.203 --> 24:32.329
